It is a bit annoying though, I have to use my regular heals/Inner fire on the chanter pet..<br>
<br>
As for it being a bug, its no worse a bug then when a cleric can duo and thus can managed to CHeal the tank while when you solo you have to use the extremly &quot;useful&quot; celestial remedy, which even then is rather useless since its so short duration and has so bad mana/hp ratio. /shrug<br>
Take a cleric and a warrior and they together are at least 5 times as efficient as they are on their own. Its not so much difference with that as the 2 pets thing really. <p>Dannor Stoutwise 42 cleric<BR>
